<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home Page</title>
<style media="screen">
/* Reset some default styles */
body, h1, h2, p, ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

/* Define basic styling */
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f7f7f7;
    color: #333;
}

header {
    background-color: #ff6f61; /* Colorful header background */
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px 0;
}

nav {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
}

.logo {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #fff; /* White text color */
}

.nav-links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
}

.nav-links li {
    margin-right: 20px;
}

.nav-links a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff; /* White text color */
    font-weight: bold;
}

/* Style the hero section */
#hero {
    background-image: url('hero-background.jpg'); /* Add your hero image here */
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 0;
    color: #fff; /* White text color */
}

#hero h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

#hero p {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 15px 30px;
    background-color: #ff6f61; /* Button color */
    color: #fff; /* Button text color */
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    border-radius: 5px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
}

.cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #ff5442; /* Hover color */
}

section {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    padding: 40px;
    background-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

h1, h2 {
    color: #333;
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
    background-color: #222;
    color: #fff;
}

/* Add more specific styles as needed */

</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
       <nav>
           <div class="logo">Mental Health</div>
           <ul class="nav-links">
               <li><a href="">HOME</a></li>
               <li><a href="">PROFILE</a></li>
               <li><a href=""></a></li>
               <li><a href="">LOG OUT</a></li>
           </ul>
       </nav>
   </header>

   <section id="hero">
       <div class="hero-content">
           <h1>Tittle</h1>
           <p>Learn to protect yourself from social engineering threats in an engaging way.</p>
           <a href="mcq" class="cta-button">Answers these questions</a>
       </div>
   </section>

   <section id="games">
       <div class="section-content">
           <h2>Educational Game</h2>
           <p>Dive into a variety of games that simulate real-world social engineering scenarios. Test your ability to spot phishing emails, identify manipulation techniques, and protect your personal information.</p>
       </div>
   </section>

   <section id="learning">
       <div class="section-content">
           <h2>Learning Made Fun</h2>
           <p>We've transformed cybersecurity education into an enjoyable experience. Our games challenge your knowledge and skills while providing valuable insights.</p>
       </div>
   </section>

   <section id="updates">
       <div class="section-content">
           <h2>Stay Updated</h2>
           <p>Keep up with the latest trends and developments in social engineering threats. Access resources, articles, and expert insights to stay informed and vigilant.</p>
       </div>
   </section>

   <footer>
       <p>&copy; 2023 Web Wizard
       </p>
   </footer>
</body>
</html>
